,"value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"美国的冬春学期五月份就结束了，毕业典礼中的 hooding ceremony 一般在此学期的最后一个周五，commencement 在接下来的周一。","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1,"offset":36},"end":{"line":7,"column":75,"offset":110}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1,"offset":36},"end":{"line":7,"column":75,"offset":110}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我早就毕业了，但是答辩的时候刚刚过了毕业典礼的日期没多久。毕业之后回了一趟家，然后返回原实验室做博士后。","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1,"offset":112},"end":{"line":9,"column":53,"offset":164}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1,"offset":112},"end":{"line":9,"column":53,"offset":164}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"hr","properties":{},"children":[],"position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1,"offset":166},"end":{"line":11,"column":4,"offset":169}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"今年春天，我们研究方向的师生每周茶聚的时候，我们老板盛赞我选择下一年的春天参加毕业典礼是个明智的选择，毕竟冬学期的活动太冷清了，都没有人重视。","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1,"offset":171},"end":{"line":13,"column":72,"offset":242}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1,"offset":171},"end":{"line":13,"column":72,"offset":242}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"当时我的面部肌肉稍微拉起来一个微笑，没有接话。","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1,"offset":244},"end":{"line":15,"column":24,"offset":267}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1,"offset":244},"end":{"line":15,"column":24,"offset":267}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这是在提醒我，他可没有忘，所以请我也不要忘了报名今年的毕业典礼哟～","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1,"offset":269},"end":{"line":17,"column":34,"offset":302}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1,"offset":269},"end":{"line":17,"column":34,"offset":302}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"刚入学的时候，我觉得我们老板怎么这么水，数学水编程也水，就这还是两校出来的学生？现在的我真心地除了佩服还是佩服，我们老板不论安排什么任务，还是讲什么知识，说起来都笑吟吟的，我认识他六年有余了，从来没见他红过脸——这个世界如此地混沌，他却能微笑着一句话，剪断一个将来可能有无限枝叶的世界线分叉——那还有多少事，多少人的“自由意志”，都包含在他的自由意志之中呢？","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1,"offset":304},"end":{"line":19,"column":180,"offset":483}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1,"offset":304},"end":{"line":19,"column":180,"offset":483}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"hr","properties":{},"children":[],"position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1,"offset":485},"end":{"line":21,"column":4,"offset":488}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"说第二年参加毕业仪式是一种“选择”，是因为至少还有两种做法：1. 答辩之前就参加当年的活动，我们组比我高一级的学姐就是这么干的；2. 毕业之后的冬季学期结束的时候还有一次 hooding ceremony, HK 兄弟就是这么干的。","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1,"offset":490},"end":{"line":23,"column":117,"offset":606}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1,"offset":490},"end":{"line":23,"column":117,"offset":606}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"两种做法我都没有选，因为我本来完全不打算参加任何毕业活动的。","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1,"offset":608},"end":{"line":25,"column":31,"offset":638}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1,"offset":608},"end":{"line":25,"column":31,"offset":638}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"毕竟对于迂腐的小知识分子，一个行为能带来的世俗荣誉感越大，做了就越庸俗，拒绝就越优雅～","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1,"offset":640},"end":{"line":27,"column":44,"offset":683}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1,"offset":640},"end":{"line":27,"column":44,"offset":683}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我们本科的毕业纪念册上，居然有一个文本框要填什么“所获荣誉”，简直是人心不古世风日下，于是咱仗义执言：“物理学院院内足球联赛亚军；BiliBili 放映室写评论赢电影票活动获奖观众”——优雅，实在是太优雅了.gif","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1,"offset":685},"end":{"line":29,"column":108,"offset":792}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1,"offset":685},"end":{"line":29,"column":108,"offset":792}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"https://syimg.3dmgame.com/uploadimg/xiaz/2022/0607/1654566377264.gif","alt":"https://syimg.3dmgame.com/uploadimg/xiaz/2022/0607/1654566377264.gif"},"children":[],"position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1,"offset":794},"end":{"line":31,"column":142,"offset":935}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1,"offset":794},"end":{"line":31,"column":142,"offset":935}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"纪念册打印出来之后我一看，律神的第一行写着“珠峰物理实验班第一学年平均分数第一名”。律神是名副其实的大学霸，大一的时候专业课都接近满分。我只是个 90 分飘过的混子，而体育课思政课之类的我又碰巧分数比他高，算 GPA 的话居然比他还高了一点点。大一下学期的电磁学期末考试实在是太简单，直接把他气到在群里@老师，大二转学到了数学班。","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1,"offset":937},"end":{"line":33,"column":166,"offset":1102}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1,"offset":937},"end":{"line":33,"column":166,"offset":1102}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"del","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"对了，数学班的班花毕业纪念册好像写得也很优雅。我自己其实真无所谓，但我有个朋友真的很想知道一下人家的联系方式。","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":3,"offset":1106},"end":{"line":35,"column":58,"offset":1161}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1,"offset":1104},"end":{"line":35,"column":60,"offset":1163}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1,"offset":1104},"end":{"line":35,"column":60,"offset":1163}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"hr","properties":{},"children":[],"position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1,"offset":1165},"end":{"line":37,"column":4,"offset"